{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"931e6618d0","title":"对广州、湖南军区报告的批示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"60e648db64","index":0,"year":1967,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"931e6618d0"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1961-1968卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2aecf6b53b","type":"title","text":"对广州、湖南军区报告的批示","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"931e6618d0"},{"id":"d3678b1156","type":"paragraph","text":"一、现将广州、湖南军区报告两个文件，发给你们希望遵照执行。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"931e6618d0"},{"id":"981dd143c7","type":"paragraph","text":"二、是错误的必须改正，如果不改正，越陷越深，到头来还得改正，威信损失就大了。及早改正威信只能比以前高。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"931e6618d0"},{"id":"5f35e63d22","type":"paragraph","text":"三、不能动动摇摇，犹犹豫豫，听老婆孩子从保守派那里来的错误话，信以为真。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"931e6618d0"},{"id":"d6d4aa2dd7","type":"paragraph","text":"四、要受得住工人、农民、学生、战士、干部的批评，加以分析，好的接受，错的改正，解释不通的，暂时搁下来将来再说。","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"931e6618d0"},{"id":"e34ab26eb9","type":"paragraph","text":"五、要坚决相信群众大多数是好的，坏人是少数，不过百分之一、二、三，这样一想什么问题也想通了。","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"931e6618d0"}],"page":{"id":"98e63b3311","publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"931e6618d0","start":591,"end":592}}}},"__N_SSG":true}